ESCAPE ARTIST: Slipping free of restraints

Category: Rogue
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Working free of ropes, handcuffs, straightjackets, and other physical
restraints. Common among performers, prisoners with practice, and
anyone whose profession occasionally ends with them tied up.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

